         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(Lines 10-17) In account with Dorion for the meat-tax at Theogonis from Thoth to Pachon, being nine months at 350 drachmas a month, 3150 dr. Paid towards this: in Hathur to the collecting office of Samareia 700 dr., in Mecheir to the collecting office of Samareia 600 dr., in Pharmouthi 325 dr., in Pachon 325 dr. Total 1950, remainder 1200 dr.</ab>
